Name: Dress Costume
Short description: Command attention as a Gothic Vampire Lord in a lavish black velvet cape, lace-trimmed coat, and dramatic accessories.
Description: Embrace the dark elegance of a Gothic Vampire Lord with this luxurious costume. The outfit features a flowing black velvet cape with blood-red lining, a high-collared coat with intricate lace details, and a pair of sleek, faux leather pants. Complete the look with a dramatic white ruffled shirt, fanged teeth, and a touch of vampire-inspired makeup.

Name: Kids' Rubble Costume
Short description: Unleash your inner beast with a Classic Werewolf costume, featuring a fur body suit, clawed gloves, and a snarling mask.
Description: Transform into a fearsome creature of the night with the Classic Werewolf costume. This ensemble includes a faux fur body suit with detailed wolf-like features, clawed gloves, and a snarling mask. The tattered clothes and exposed fur make it look like you’ve just emerged from a full moon transformation.

Name: Kids' Dress Costume
Short description: Rock the undead look with a Retro 80s Zombie costume, featuring a neon jumpsuit, faux blood, and vintage-style face paint.
Description: Get ready to scare in style with the Retro 80s Zombie costume. This look features a neon-colored, torn-up jumpsuit reminiscent of the vibrant 80s fashion, complete with faux blood splatters and strategic rips. The accompanying face paint and wig complete the look, giving you a totally tubular undead appearance.

Name: Halloween Costume
Short description: Lead the haunted show as a Circus Ringmaster with a tattered tailcoat, spooky top hat, and eerie cane.
Description: Step into the macabre with the Haunted Circus Ringmaster costume. This outfit includes a black and red tailcoat with eerie, tattered edges, a top hat with a spooky touch, and a dramatic bowtie. The ringmaster’s gloves and cane add a final touch to your sinister circus persona.

Name: Woman in Black Witch Costume
Short description: Bring magic to life with the Forest Fairy costume, featuring a flower-adorned dress, shimmering wings, and a whimsical crown.
Description: Delight and enchant with the Forest Fairy costume, which includes a delicate green and gold dress adorned with leaf and flower details. The costume features wings that shimmer in the light and a flower crown that adds a whimsical touch. Perfect for spreading magic and wonder.

Name: Student Killer Costume
Short description: Embrace the future with a Cyberpunk Android costume, featuring a metallic bodysuit, LED accents, and a high-tech visor.
Description: Futuristic and edgy, the Cyberpunk Android costume features a sleek metallic bodysuit with LED accents, a high-tech visor, and robotic gloves. The design merges neon colors with a cutting-edge, tech-inspired look, ideal for those who want to make a bold statement at any Halloween event.

Name: Frankie stein costume
Short description: Haunt with style in a Classic Ghost costume featuring a glowing, ethereal white sheet and LED-lit edges.
Description: This Classic Ghost costume gets a modern upgrade with LED-lit edges and a flowy, ethereal fabric. The costume includes a traditional white sheet with a spooky glow, creating a hauntingly beautiful appearance that’s perfect for both scares and style.

Name: Cauldron treat bucket
Short description: Go wild as a Mad Scientist with a lab coat, wild wig, goggles, and rubber test tubes for a truly zany look.
Description: Unleash your inner genius with the Mad Scientist costume, complete with a white lab coat splattered with faux “experiments,” a wild wig, and goggles. Accessories include rubber test tubes and beakers, adding an extra layer of crazy to your look as you create chaos in your laboratory.
